content:
Product Service Campaigns for Vehicle and Parts Recalls

Organize product service campaigns to service faulty products, recall defective assets, and manage outreach campaigns at scale. Service managers can create and manage effective campaigns, nurture customer trust, and ensure customer safety.

Manage Asset Recalls and Upgrades At Scale
Design timely product service campaigns to effectively assess and address issues on large numbers of products or services. Specify the impacted product, and the priority, duration, status, and type of a campaign. Create work orders and return orders to capture the services to be performed on impacted products.

Segment Assets for Product Service Campaigns Easily
Automotive service teams are no longer required to identify faulty assets and individually add them to product service campaigns. Service managers can now identify, segment, and add a large number of assets in an actionable list. 

Service managers can use filter conditions or Data Cloud segments to group assets that are included in actionable lists. They can assign the lists to service agents for engagement initiatives and outreach campaigns.
title: Product Service Campaigns for Vehicle and Parts Recalls
